1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO MAKE VARIOUS CHANGES TO THE PRINCIPAL FELLOWS PROGRAM
3 AND TO PROVIDE REQUIREMENTS FOR STIPENDS FOR THE MASTER'S IN
4 SCHOOL ADMINISTRATION INTERNSHIP.
5 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
