1 (2) The sum of two million four hundred thousand dollars ($2,400,000) to expand
2 the number of principal fellows candidates supported by the Program with the
3 goal of having fifty-five percent (55%) of all principals employed in North
4 Carolina be graduates of the North Carolina Principal Fellows Program.
